VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:application-settings|ApplicationSettings\.set|setString\s*\()
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:ApplicationSettings\.setString.*(?:password|token|secret|key|credential)|getString.*(?:password|token|secret|key|credential)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects persistence APIs commonly used for local settings storage.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Weak Local Secret Storage.
